@startuml BristolWest_AutoQuote_ComponentDiagram

title Bristol West (Farmers Insurance)\nAuto Insurance Quotation System — Architecture Overview

skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam nodesep 40
skinparam ranksep 50
skinparam padding 8

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor<<frontend>>   #DDEEFF
  BorderColor<<frontend>>       #336699
  FontColor<<frontend>>         #003366
  FontStyle<<frontend>>         bold

  BackgroundColor<<gateway>>    #FFF3CC
  BorderColor<<gateway>>        #CC9900
  FontColor<<gateway>>          #664400
  FontStyle<<gateway>>          bold

  BackgroundColor<<service>>    #E6F4EA
  BorderColor<<service>>        #2E7D32
  FontColor<<service>>          #1B5E20
  FontStyle<<service>>          bold

  BackgroundColor<<registry>>   #F3E5F5
  BorderColor<<registry>>       #7B1FA2
  FontColor<<registry>>         #4A148C
  FontStyle<<registry>>         bold

  BackgroundColor<<messaging>>  #E8EAF6
  BorderColor<<messaging>>      #283593
  FontColor<<messaging>>        #1A237E
  FontStyle<<messaging>>        bold

  BackgroundColor<<external>>   #F5F5F5
  BorderColor<<external>>       #9E9E9E
  FontColor<<external>>         #424242
}

' ─────────────────────────────────────────
' ACTOR
' ─────────────────────────────────────────
actor "Customer" as USER

' ─────────────────────────────────────────
' COMPONENTS
' ─────────────────────────────────────────
[React Frontend\n:3000] <<frontend>>      as FRONTEND
[API Gateway\n:8080] <<gateway>>          as GATEWAY
[Eureka Server\n:8761] <<registry>>       as EUREKA

[Customer Service\n:8081] <<service>>     as CUST
[Vehicle Service\n:8082] <<service>>      as VEH
[Driver Service\n:8083] <<service>>       as DRV
[Rating Service\n:8084] <<service>>       as RATING
[Quote Service\n:8085] <<service>>        as QUOTE
[Notification Service\n:8086] <<service>> as NOTIF

[Kafka\n:9092] <<messaging>>              as KAFKA
[SMTP Server] <<external>>                as SMTP

' ─────────────────────────────────────────
' FLOW
' ─────────────────────────────────────────
USER     --> FRONTEND : Get a Quote

FRONTEND --> GATEWAY  : REST (JSON)\nFinal Quote Request
FRONTEND -[#1565C0,dashed,thickness=2]-> GATEWAY : Real-Time Preview\n(debounced 300ms)

note on link
  Triggered on Step 3 & Step 4\nuser input changes
end note

GATEWAY  --> CUST     : /api/customers
GATEWAY  --> VEH      : /api/vehicles
GATEWAY  --> DRV      : /api/drivers
GATEWAY  --> QUOTE    : /api/quotes
GATEWAY  -[#1565C0,dashed,thickness=2]-> RATING : /api/rating/preview\n(real-time)
GATEWAY  --> RATING   : /api/rating/calculate\n(final quote)

QUOTE    --> CUST     : Feign
QUOTE    --> VEH      : Feign
QUOTE    --> DRV      : Feign
QUOTE    --> RATING   : Feign (final)

RATING   -[#1565C0,dashed,thickness=2]-> FRONTEND : RatingPreviewDTO\n(price panel update)

QUOTE    --> KAFKA    : publish event
KAFKA    --> NOTIF    : consume event
NOTIF    --> SMTP     : send email

GATEWAY  ..> EUREKA   : discovers
CUST     ..> EUREKA   : registers
VEH      ..> EUREKA   : registers
DRV      ..> EUREKA   : registers
RATING   ..> EUREKA   : registers
QUOTE    ..> EUREKA   : registers
NOTIF    ..> EUREKA   : registers

' ─────────────────────────────────────────
' LEGEND
' ─────────────────────────────────────────
legend right
  |= Symbol                      |= Meaning                         |
  | -->                          | Runtime call (REST / Feign / Kafka) |
  | <color:#1565C0>- - -></color>| Real-Time Pricing Preview (debounced) |
  | ..>                          | Eureka registration               |
  |<#DDEEFF>                     | React Frontend                   |
  |<#FFF3CC>                     | API Gateway                      |
  |<#E6F4EA>                     | Spring Boot Services             |
  |<#F3E5F5>                     | Eureka Discovery                 |
  |<#E8EAF6>                     | Kafka Messaging                  |
endlegend

@enduml
